{"arkId":"cl010490781","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010490781","modified ":"2026-02-19","title":"Calice","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Calice"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1598 - 1599","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 521 - Bernard Palissy","room":"Salle 521, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1598,"endYear":1599,"imprecision":"","text":"Fin du XVIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Crochet, Jean","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Orf\u00e8vre","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"RFML.OA.2021.27.1","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"calice ; orf\u00e8vrerie, argenterie","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Le calice repose sur un pied circulaire agr\u00e9ment\u00e9 de dix lobes semi-circulaires dont la tranche est estamp\u00e9e d\u2019une frise de fleurs et de rinceaux et orn\u00e9e de t\u00eates d\u2019anges en haut relief. Le dessus du pied pr\u00e9sente un d\u00e9cor repouss\u00e9 de seize grandes flammes rayonnantes alternant avec le chiffre IHS, la croix et les clous et dans un petit encadrement ovale d\u0027 une plaque d\u2019argent dor\u00e9 estamp\u00e9e d\u2019une crucifixion, avec la Vierge et saint Jean. La tige cylindrique du calice est sem\u00e9e de fleurs de lys repouss\u00e9es. Le n\u0153ud, est repouss\u00e9 d\u2019un d\u00e9cor de feuilles d\u2019acanthe enserrant huit bossettes circulaires o\u00f9 sont ins\u00e9r\u00e9s les bustes de sept ap\u00f4tres et de J\u00e9sus grav\u00e9s et rev\u00eatus d\u2019\u00e9maux translucides bleus, turquoise, verts, orange et mauves. La coupe, est doubl\u00e9e jusqu\u2019aux trois-quarts de sa hauteur d\u2019une fausse coupe repouss\u00e9e et cisel\u00e9e de flammes et de fleurs de lis.","inscriptions":"Inscription : \r ; Lettres capitales \u00ab N. L. M. \u00bb grav\u00e9es sous un lobe du pied du calice\r ; Poin\u00e7on : \r ; Ma\u00eetre : fleur de lis couronn\u00e9e, deux grains, lettre IC et un tr\u00e8fle au-dessous, pour Jean Crochet ; Jurande : lettre A couronn\u00e9e, pour d\u00e9cembre 1598-d\u00e9cembre 1599","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"23,2","displayDimension":"23,2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"15,8","displayDimension":"15,8 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"10,3","displayDimension":"10,3 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : vermeil = argent dor\u00e9 (et \u00e9maill\u00e9)\r\nTechnique : \u00e9mail translucide (techniques m\u00e9tal-\u003E\u00e9maill\u00e9 = \u00e9maillage = \u00e9mail = \u00e9maux)","placeOfCreation":"Paris (France-\u003EIle-de-France = Ile de France)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Acquis avec le concours du Cercle des M\u00e9c\u00e8nes des Objets d\u0027art, 2021","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"achat","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date d\u0027affectation","value":"13\/10\/2021","startYear":2021,"endYear":2021},{"type":"date de d\u00e9cision","value":"13\/10\/2021","startYear":2021,"endYear":2021},{"type":"date de l\u0027inscription sur l\u0027inventaire","value":"13\/10\/2021","startYear":2021,"endYear":2021},{"type":"date de d\u00e9cision","value":"13\/10\/2021","startYear":2021,"endYea